text:
Actual conversation once. 

“Are you that Mark Simpson?”
“No, no I’m not, sorry.”
“G’wan, you are.”
“No I’m really not...”
(Pause)
“D’you not wish you were him sometimes?”

(Yes .@BBCMarkSimpson I yearn for it)
